quran[227]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,"Twaa Siin Miim."
  26,2,"Izi, ni Aayah z’Igitabu Qor’ani gitomoye neza; mu nsiguro, mu ngingo z’ibirekuwe n’ibizira, no mu burongozi bwaco."
  26,3,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Biragaragara ko utuntuzwa umutima n’uko abantu bataraba abemeramana ngo bagukurikire, mpore ntugatunture ku mutima!"
  26,4,"Twebwe Allah, Dushatse Twomanurira abaguhakana bivuye inyuma mu bantu warungitsweko, igitangaro kivuye mw’ijuru cotuma bemera ku nabi ku neza, maze bakama bicishije bugufi, ariko rero ntitwashatse ko biba ukwo, kuko ukwemera Imana Allah nya kwemera kuba ku bushake ata gahato kagiyemwo."
  26,5,"Ababangikanyamana, ntibigera bashikirwa n’inkebuzo nshasha ivuye kwa Nyenimpuhwe Allah, ibabwiriza ivyo bakora n’ivyo bareka mu kwubahiriza idini ry’ukuri, kiretse ko birengagiza nya nkebuzo, bakayihakana bivuye inyuma, bakanayamirira kure."
  26,6,"Ni ukuri, ababangikanyamana barahakanye Qor’ani baranayiteburako. Kubera ivyo rero, bitebe bitebuke, bazoshikirwa n’ukuri kw’inkuru z’ivyo bateburako, maze bahanwe."
  26,7,"Mbega ntibaraba isi ngo babone ukuntu Twayinagishijeko ibimera vyinshi ngirakamaro, biri mu bwoko bwose bw’ibiterwa n'ivyimeza, ata wushoboye kubinagisha atari Imana Allah!"
  26,8,"Mu vy’ukuri mw’inagishwa ry’ivyo vyose, ni ukuri harimwo icemezo cerekana ubushobozi n'ububasha vy’Imana Allah, burya abenshi mu bantu, si abemeramana namba;"
  26,9,"Kandi mu vy’ukuri Imana yawe Rurema Allah, ni ukuri, ni Yo Nyenintsinzi-Mutaneshwa, Nyenimbabazi ku batoni bayo."
  26,10,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Cira agace abo warungitsweko ku nkuru ya Musa, igihe Imana yawe Rurema Allah Yahamagara Musa Iti: “Genda ku bantu birenganije;"
  26,11,"Abantu ba Firawuni, maze ubararikire kugamburukira Imana Allah mu gushira mu ngiro amabwirizwa yayo”."
  26,12,"Musa yavuze ati: “Mana yanje Rurema Allah! Jewe ndafise impungenge ko bohakana bivuye inyuma ubutumwa ndabazaniye;"
  26,13,"Ngatuntuzwa n’uko bangararije, kandi n’ururimi rwanje ntirutomora bikwiye, ndagusavye rero Uhe ubutumwa murumunanje Haruna kugira anshigikire, yongere anyunganire mu kubumvisha ubutumwa nzoba ndabashikirije;"
  26,14,"Hari n’igicumuro nabakoreye co kwica umuntu mu Banyagiputa, ndatinya rero ko boca bamwihorera, bakanyica”."
  26,15,"Imana Allah Yabwiye Musa Iti: “Ihibambewe! Tekana nta co bazokugira. Na murumunawe Haruna Tumugize Intumwa, nimugende rero uko muri babiri mwitwaje ibitangaro vyacu Twebwe Allah, vyerekana ukuri kwanyu; mu vy’ukuri, Turi kumwe na mwe ku bumenyi bwacu no mu kubabungabunga, Turumviriza n’ivyo mushikiriza;"
  26,16,"Enda nyabuna rero, nimugende kwa Firawuni, maze mumubwire muti: “Twebwe mu vy’ukuri, turi Intumwa zirungitswe n’Imana yawe Rurema Allah kuri wewe no ku bantu bawe;"
  26,17,"Ko wobohora Bene Israyeli ukareka kubacinyiza, tugaheza rero tukabarongora mu nzira y’Imana Allah, bakadukurikira””."
  26,18,"Firawuni yishuye Musa n’agashinyaguro n'akantu ati: “Mbega uribagiye ko twakurereye ng’aha kuva ukiri uruyoya, uraheza ubana na twe imyaka n’iyindi!"
  26,19,"Uraheza ukora igicumuro co kwica Umunyagiputa igihe winamura umukubita igipfunsi, aca ararambarara! Ako, ni ko gashimwe wampaye ku ciza nagukoreye co kukurera!”."
  26,20,"Musa araheza yishura Firawuni ati: “Nimba ico gicumuro naragikoze, sinari bwahishurirwe kuba Intumwa!"
  26,21,"Ni naho nata nkomoka mpungira i Madiyana, ku gutinya ko mwonyica mwihorera Umunyagiputa wanyu nishe kw’isanganya; mu nyuma, Imana yanje Rurema Allah Yahavuye Impa ubutumwa n’ubumenyi, maze Ingira Intumwa mu zindi;"
  26,22,"Iryo rererwa ryanje iwawe na ryo unshinyagurizako, ryabaye kugira ngo ubandanye ucura bufuni na buhoro Bene Israyeli!”."
  26,23,"Firawuni yahavuye abaza Musa ati: “Imana Rurema w’ibiremwa vyose Yakurungitse, ni igiki?”."
  26,24,"Musa yavuze yishura Firawuni ati: “Ni Imana Rurema, Umubungabunzi w’amajuru n’isi hamwe n’ibiri hagati yavyo; nimwaba rero muzi neza ivyo, nimuyemere”."
  26,25,"Firawuni arinamura abwira abubahwa bari ng’aho bamukikije ati: “Muranyumvira ako kamaramaza ka Musa, aho yubahuka akavuga ko hari iyindi mana atari jewe!”."
  26,26,"Musa yarongeye avuga kandi ati: “Imana ndabararikira kwemera, ni Imana yanyu Rurema Allah Yabaremye, Ikanarema ba so mukomokako”."
  26,27,"Firawuni n’ishavu n’akantu asubizayo anebagura Musa ati: “Mu vy’ukuri Intumwa yanyu mwarungikiwe, ni ukuri, ni umusazi, ivuga ibitaroranye namba”."
  26,28,"Musa arongera ati: “Imana ndabararikira kwemera, ni Imana Rurema Yaremye ubuseruko n’uburengero hamwe n’ibiri hagati yavyo; Irema n’umuco n’umuzimagiza. Ivyo rero, bikaba ari ivyemezo vy’uko ari Yo Ikwiye kwemerwa no gusengwa ari Imwe Rudende nimwaba mutegera neza ububasha bwayo”."
  26,29,"Firawuni aca avuga n’iterabwoba n’akantu yihaniza Musa ati: “Niwigenera Iyindi Mana atari jewe, ni ukuri ntegerezwa kuguta mw’ibohero hamwe n’abandi”."
  26,30,"Musa asubizayo ati: “Mbega uraheza unte mw’ibohero hamwe n’abandi, n’aho nokuzanira icemezo gitomoye ko ndi mu kuri!”."
  26,31,"Firawuni aca asaba Musa ko yozana icemezo ati: “Enda nyabuna rero, zana ico cemezo ku vyo uvuga niwaba uri mu mvugakuri ko uri Intumwa vy’ukuri”."
  26,32,"Ni ho rero Musa yaterera inkoni yiwe hasi, ica ihinduka inzoka amahanga yigendera, abantu birabira;"
  26,33,"Araheza kandi ashira ikiganza ciwe mu kwaha, agize ngo aragikuyeyo, caje cererana gisayangana cane abari ng’aho birabira, barumirwa."
  26,34,"Firawuni aca agira impungenge z’uko abunganizi bari ng’aho bamukikije, bohava banyurwa bakemera, araheza ababwira ati: “Mu vy’ukuri, Musa nta nkeka ko ari umukonikoni karuhariwe;"
  26,35,"Ashaka kubomora mwese abakure mu gihugu canyu akoresheje ubukonikoni bwiwe, none rero mumpanuye ko nokora iki?”."
  26,36,"Abunganizi bari hambavu ya Firawuni bavuze bamuhanura bati: “Musa na murumunawe Haruna, bahe irindi sango ryo guhurirako, maze utume abararika abantu mu bisagara vyose vyo muri Misiri;"
  26,37,"Baheze begeranye zina mukonikoni wese karuhariwe, bamukuzanire”."
  26,38,"Ni ho rero abakonikoni bose bakoranirizwa hamwe ku musi w’isango nyezina;"
  26,39,"Abararitsi baraheza bararika abantu bati: “Nyabuna nyabuna nimwitabire ikoraniro ku bwinshi kugira mushigikire abakonikoni!"
  26,40,"Hari n’aho twotsimbatara kw’idini rya Firawuni, tugakurikira abakonikoni mu gihe boramuka batsinze”."
  26,41,"Umusi w’isango ugeze, nya bakonikoni karuhariwe bariyegeranije bashika kwa Firawuni, bamubaza bati: “Mbega none, ubwo duhava turonka agashimwe gashimishije, nitwaramuka dutsinze Musa?”."
  26,42,"Firawuni na we abishura ati: “Ego cane! Kandi muri ico gihe muzoba muri no mu batoni b’abishikira bari hambavu yanje”."
  26,43,"Musa yabariye nya bakonikoni ashaka ko ikinyoma gikubitirwa ahashashe ati: “Nimuterere hasi ivyo mushaka mu bukonikoni bwanyu”."
  26,44,"Ni ho rero nya bakonikoni baterera imizana n’inkoni vyabo hasi, barahunika abantu bose bari ng’aho, ntibaba bakibona nya mizana na nya nkoni nk’uko bisanzwe, ahubwo babona inzoka, baraheza barahira kw’izina rya Firawuni bavuga bati: “Mu cubahiro ca Firawuni, ni ukuri dutegerezwa gutsinda Musa”."
  26,45,"Ni ho Musa rero yaterera inkoni yiwe hasi, nya nkoni ica ihinduka inzoka amahanga yigendera, ya nzoka ica imiragura ivyo batereye hasi vyose, ivyari vyakanze abantu babona ko ari inzoka vy’ukuri kandi ari ikinyoma ceruye."
  26,46,"Ba bakonikoni bamaze kubona ico gitangaro c’inkoni, baciye bubamira Imana Allah;"
  26,47,"Bavuga bati: “Twemeye Imana Rurema, Umubungabunzi w’ibiremwa vyose;"
  26,48,"Imana Rurema ya Musa na murumunawe Haruna”."
  26,49,"Firawuni n’ishavu n’akantu yaciye avuga abiyamiriza ati: “Mbega karashize ingani mwemere Iyo Mana ya Musa, imbere yuko ndabibarekurira! Mu vy’ukuri biragaragaye ko Musa, ari we mukuru wanyu yabigishije ubukonikoni. Kubera ivyo rero, mugiye kwibonerako ayo imbwa yaboneye ku mugezi; ntegerezwa kubaca amaboko n’amaguru binyuranije; ndabace ukuboko kw’ukuryo hamwe n’ukuguru kw’ukubamfu, ukuboko kw’ukubamfu hamwe n’ukuguru kw’ukuryo, hanyuma mpeze ndababambe mwese ku bishitsi vy’igiti”."
  26,50,"Ba bakonikoni, baraheza bishura Firawuni bati: “Nta co bidutwaye namba, twebwe mu vy’ukuri, uramutse utwishe dusubira ku Mana yacu Rurema Allah;"
  26,51,"Mu vy’ukuri, twebwe turizeye ko Imana yacu Rurema Allah, Itugumiriza akabanga, Ikatubabarira ivyaha vyacu, kuko tubaye aba mbere bayemeye mu bantu bawe”."
  26,52,"Ni ho rero Twebwe Allah Twahishurira Musa Tumubwira Duti: “Genda muri iri joro ujanye abaja banje bemeye muri Bene Israyeli, kuko mu vy’ukuri Firawuni n’ingabo ziwe, bahava babakurikira ngo babafate imbere yuko mujabuka ibahari”."
  26,53,"Firawuni yaciye arungika abararitsi mu bisagara vyose kwegeranya ingabo ziwe;"
  26,54,"Araheza avuga ati: “Bene Israyeli bahunganye na Musa, ni akagwi k’abantu bari ku rushi, bagayitse;"
  26,55,"Kandi mu vy’ukuri, baraduteye ishavu ryinshi ku guca kubiri n’idini ryacu;"
  26,56,"Na twe rero turarikanuye ntibaducarukana”."
  26,57,"Ni ho rero Twebwe Allah, Twakura Firawuni hamwe n’abantu biwe mu gihugu ca Misiri kirangwa n’imirima itotahaye n’amazi y’amariba atemba;"
  26,58,"Hari n’ibigega vy’ubutunzi n’inyubakwa ziteye igomwe."
  26,59,"Ni nk’uko nyene rero Twebwe Allah - Twabakuye muri ico gihugu ca Misiri - Twahavuye Tukiraga mu nyuma Bene Israyeli."
  26,60,"Firawuni rero hamwe n’ingabo ziwe, bahavuye bakurikira Musa n’abo bari kumwe mu mutwenzi."
  26,61,"Bamaze guhura na bo amaso mu yandi, abantu ba Musa n’ubwoba n’akantu bavuze bati: “Musa, ni ukuri abantu ba Firawuni nta kibuza baradufashe, turahonye!”."
  26,62,"Musa yabishuye ati: “Kizire, ntibagenda babafashe namba kuko ndi kumwe n’Imana yanje Rurema Allah mu kuntabara, Irandongora inzira idukura muri aka kaga”."
  26,63,"Ni ho rero Twebwe Allah Twahishurira Musa Tumubwira Duti: “Kubita iyo nkoni yawe kw’ibahari”. Ubwo nyene ya bahari yicamwo inzira cumi na zibiri; zihuriranye n’igitigiri kingana n’amoko ya Bene Israyeli, maze igice cose c’ibahari kigabura inzira n’iyindi kiba nk’umusozi amahanga."
  26,64,"Aho rero, ni ho Twashorera Firawuni n’ingabo ziwe gushika n’aho binjira mw’ibahari bibwira ngo bakurikiye Musa n’abo bari kumwe;"
  26,65,"Turaheza Turokora Musa n’abo bari kumwe bose, barajabuka amahoro gushika ku rundi ruhande rw’ibahari."
  26,66,"Mu nyuma, ni ho nya bahari yasubira guterana, maze Twebwe Allah Duca Dusomesha nturi Firawuni n’ingabo ziwe, bahonera rimwe."
  26,67,"Mu vy’ukuri, muri ivyo vyashikiye Firawuni n’ingabo ziwe, ni ukuri harimwo inkebuzo yerekena koko ubushobozi n'ububasha vy’Imana Allah. Hamwe n’ivyo rero, abenshi mu bakurikira Firawuni ntibahavuye bemera."
  26,68,"Ntumwa y'Imana! Mu vy’ukuri Imana yawe Rurema Allah, ni ukuri ni Yo Nyenintsinzi-Mutaneshwa, Nyenimbabazi ku batoni bayo."
  26,69,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Cira ku mayange abagarariji, inkuru ya Ibrahimu;"
  26,70,"Igihe yabwira se hamwe n’abantu biwe ati: “Ni igiki musenga?”."
  26,71,"Bavuze bamwishura bati: “Dusenga ibigirwamana, tugaheza tukavyiyegurira”."
  26,72,"Ibrahimu yababwiye abanebagura ati: “None burya, ivyo bigirwamana biraheza bikabumvira igisabisho iyo mubisavye?"
  26,73,"Canke bikagira ico bibamariye iyo mubisenze? Canke bikagira ico bibiciye iyo mutabisenze?”."
  26,74,"Bavuze bamwishura bati: “Eka nta na kimwe tuziga kuri ivyo bigirwamana! Ahubwo twasanze abavyeyi bacu babisenga, na twe tubisenga ukwo”."
  26,75,"Ibrahimu yavuze ati: “Mbe burya muraraba mukazirikana ivyo musenga;"
  26,76,"Mwebwe hamwe n’abavyeyi banyu b’abakurambere!"
  26,77,"Mu vy’ukuri ivyo musenga mu gishingo c'Imana Allah, vyose ni abansi kuri jewe, ariko Imana Rurema w’ibiremwa vyose, ni Yo gusa nsenga;"
  26,78,"Ni Yo Yandemye mw’ishusho ryiza, Iraheza Irandongora mu gukora ibimfitiye akamaro kw’isi no mu buzima bw’inyuma yo gupfa;"
  26,79,"Ni na Yo Indonsa imfugurwa Ikandonsa n’ico nywa;"
  26,80,"N’iyo ndwaye, ni Yo Inkiza nkaroranirwa mu magara;"
  26,81,"Ni na Yo Inyaka ubuzima kw’isi ngapfa, hanyuma Ikazonsubiza kandi ubuzima ku musi w’izuka, nkazuka;"
  26,82,"Ni na Yo nizeye ko Ingumiriza akabanga Ikazombabarira ivyaha vyanje ku musi w’impera”."
  26,83,"Ibrahimu yavuze asaba ati: “Mana yanje Rurema Allah! Mpa ubumenyi no gutahura bikwiye, Wongere Unkurikize aberanda tuzohurira mu Bwami bw’ijuru;"
  26,84,"Umpe no kuyagwa neza n’abantu mu bazokurikira gushika ku musi w’iherezo;"
  26,85,"Unshire no mu baja bawe Wageneye Ubwami bw’ijuru bwuzuye inema;"
  26,86,"Urongore n’umuvyeyi wanje mu nzira yawe, maze Umugumirize akabanga, Umubabarire ivyaha vyiwe; mu vy’ukuri, yari mu bantu bahuvye;"
  26,87,"Kandi ntuzontetereze umusi ibiremwa vyazutse kugira biharurirwe, maze bigahemberwa ivyo vyakoze;"
  26,88,"Umusi amatungo n’ibibondo ata na kimwe bizomarira umuntu;"
  26,89,"Kiretse umuntu azoza ku Mana Allah arangwa n’umutima wejejwe ubugarariji n’uburyarya”."
  26,90,"Kuri nya musi rero, Ubwami bw’ijuru buzokwegerezwa abagamburukiramana;"
  26,91,"Umuriro ururumba na wo, ushirirwe ahabona abarenze ku mabwirizwa y’Imana Allah, bakanahakana bivuye inyuma Intumwa zayo;"
  26,92,"Maze babwirwe n’agashinyaguro n'akantu bati: “Mbega ibigirwamana mwahora musenga mu gishingo c’Imana Allah, biri hehe ngo bibavugire kuri uno musi!"
  26,93,"Mbega burya nya bigirwamana birashoboye kubatabara ngo bibakureko ibihano! Mbe hoho nya bigirwamana nyene biranashoboye kwikura mu bihano!”."
  26,94,"Bazoheza rero begeranirizwe hamwe, maze batabwe mu muriro batanguje umutwe, bari mu migwimigwi. Nya bigirwamana hamwe n’abarenze ku mabwirizwa y’Imana Allah bakanahakana n’Intumwa zayo, bazotabwa muri nya muriro;"
  26,95,"Bari kumwe n’ababahubishije mu ngabo za shetani zabaryohereza gukora ibibi, nta n’umwe azocaruka."
  26,96,"Bazohazana bari mu muriro ku makosa yabo;"
  26,97,"Bavuga babwira ababahubushije bati: “Turarahiye kw’izina ry’Imana Allah! Ni ukuri, kw’isi twari mu buhuvyi bugaragara;"
  26,98,"Mu kubasenga tubanganisha n’Imana Rurema w’ibiremwa vyose, Ikwiye gusengwa ari Imwe Rudende;"
  26,99,"Burya nta cadukwegeye akaga kikadushikana aha turi, kiretse abanyavyaha barenga ku mabwirizwa y’Imana Allah baduhubishije, tukabumvira;"
  26,100,"Ubwo none ga yemwe! Nta n’umwe yonadusabira akadukura muri ibi bihano turimwo!"
  26,101,"Nta n’umugenzi nkoramutima yotwumvira n’ikigongwe!"
  26,102,"Ese twopfuma dusubizwa kandi kw’isi tugaheza tukaba abemeramana koko!”."
  26,103,"Mu vy’ukuri mu nkuru ya Ibrahimu, ni ukuri harimwo inkebuzo ku wumva akikebuka. Hamwe n’ivyo rero, abenshi mu bashikiriwe n’iyo nkuru ntibahavuye bemera."
  26,104,"Mu vy’ukuri Imana yawe Rurema Allah, ni ukuri ni Yo Nyenintsinzi-Mutaneshwa, Nyenimbabazi ku batoni bayo."
  26,105,"Abantu barungikiwe Intumwa Nuhu barahakanye bivuye inyuma Intumwa yabo, baca bafatwa nk’aho bahakanye Intumwa zose;"
  26,106,"Igihe mwenewabo Nuhu yababwira ati: “Ubwo ntimwogamburukira Imana Allah mukubahiriza ibwirizwa ryo kuyisenga ari Imwe Rudende!"
  26,107,"Mu vy’ukuri, jewe kuri mwebwe ndi Intumwa, nkaba n’Umwizigirwa mu vyo ndabashikiriza;"
  26,108,"Enda rero nyabuna nimwikingire ibihano vy’Imana Allah mu kunyemera, muheze munyumvire mu gusenga Imana Imwe Rudende Allah;"
  26,109,"Nta mpembo ndabasavye kw’ishikirizabutumwa ryanje, impembo yanje ndayiziga ku Mana Rurema Allah, Yo Mubungabunzi w’ibiremwa vyose;"
  26,110,"Kubera ivyo rero, nimwikingire ibihano vy’Imana Allah mu kunyemera, muheze munyumvire mu gushira mu ngiro amabwirizwa yayo""."
  26,111,"Abantu ba Nuhu barinamuye bati: “Wewe ubona twokwemera gute ngo tugukurikire mu gihe wakurikiwe n’abantu ba nyarucari n’imbunuza!”."
  26,112,"Nuhu (nyakugira amahoro y’Imana Allah) araheza abishura ati: “Sinjejwe kumenya ubuzima babayemwo; ico njejwe, ni ukubararikira ukwemera, burya ubutore n’icubahiro c’umuntu, biva ku kwemera Imana Allah, ntibiva ku muryango canke ku co ari mu kibano;"
  26,113,"Iharurirwa ryabo ku vyo bakoze, rijejwe Imana yanje Rurema Allah. Iyo muba muzi ko biri ukwo rero, ntimwari kunebagura abankurikiye;"
  26,114,"Kandi nanje nyene sindota nirukana abemeramana bankurikiye uko bari kwose kugira ngo munyemere;"
  26,115,"Jewe burya nta kindi njejwe, kiretse ko ndi Umugabisha atomoye ku bihano vy’Imana Allah”."
  26,116,"Abantu ba Nuhu bahavuye bamutera ubwoba bati: “Nuhu! Utaretse iryo rarikiramana ryawe, ni ukuri nta kibuza, tuzokwicisha amabuye!”."
  26,117,"Nuhu amaze kwumva iterabwoba ryabo, yaratakambiye Imana Allah avuga ati: “Mana yanje Rurema Allah! Mu vy’ukuri abantu banje Wandungitseko, bangararije bimwe biboneka;"
  26,118,"Ndagusavye rero ko Ufata ingingo idutandukanya mu guhonya abaguhakana bakagarariza Intumwa yawe, maze Undokore muri iryo honywa jewe hamwe n’abo turi kumwe mu bemeramana”."
  26,119,"Imana Allah Yarumviye Nuhu, maze Iramurokora muri nya honywa we hamwe n’abari kumwe na we mu bwato bwarimwo amoko yose y’ibiremwa."
  26,120,"Mu nyuma rero, ni ho Twebwe Allah Twahonya abahakanye bakagarariza."
  26,121,"Mu vy’ukuri, mu nkuru ya Nuhu n’ihonywa ry’abamugararije, ni ukuri harimwo inkebuzo ku bantu. Hamwe n’ivyo rero, abenshi mu bashikiriwe n’iyo nkuru, ntibahavuye bemera Imana Allah n’Intumwa zayo ngo bubahirize n’amabwirizwa yayo."
  26,122,"Mu vy’ukuri Imana yawe Rurema Allah, ni ukuri ni Yo Nyenintsinzi-Mutaneshwa, Nyenimbabazi ku batoni bayo."
  26,123,"Bene Aadi barahakanye bivuye inyuma Intumwa yabo Huudi, baca bafatwa nk’aho bahakanye Intumwa zose."
  26,124,"Igihe mwenewabo Huudi yababwira ati: “Ubwo ntimwogamburukira Imana Allah mukubahiriza ibwirizwa ryo kuyisenga ari Imwe Rudende!;"
  26,125,"Mu vy’ukuri, jewe kuri mwebwe ndi Intumwa, nkaba n’Umwizigirwa mu vyo ndabashikiriza;"
  26,126,"Enda rero nyabuna nimwikingire ibihano vy’Imana Allah mu kunyemera, muheze munyumvire mu kwubahiriza amabwirizwa y’Imana Allah;"
  26,127,"Nta mpembo ndabasavye kw’ishikirizabutumwa ryanje, impembo yanje ndayiziga ku Mana Rurema Allah, Yo Mubungabunzi w’ibiremwa vyose,"
  26,128,"Mbega mwubaka inyubakwa ndende aho hose hataramutse, mu ntumbero yo kwihambaza mukengera abarengana hepfo yanyu!"
  26,129,"Mukigirira n’amazu y’intamenwa y’amagorofa; nk’aho muzokwama kw’isi ibihe bidahera;"
  26,130,"N’iyo hagize uwo mucakira mu bantu mukamukubita canke mukamwica, mubikora ku kagagazo n’akarenganyo;"
  26,131,"Kubera ivyo rero, nimwikingire ibihano vy’Imana Allah mu kunyemera, muheze munyumvire mu gushira mu ngiro amabwirizwa yayo;"
  26,132,"Muheze mugamburukire Imana Allah Yabahaye inema muzi z’ubwoko bwose;"
  26,133,"Yabahaye ibitungwa, Ibaha n’ibibondo;"
  26,134,"Ibaha n’imirima itotahaye hamwe n’amazi y’amariba atemba”."
  26,135,"Huudi (nyakugira amahoro y’Imana Allah) yarihanije abantu yarungitsweko ati: “Mu vy’ukuri, jewe ndatinya ko mwoshikirwa n’ibihano vy’Imana Allah ku musi uhambaye, mu gihe mworendegera mu bugarariji, mwihakana n’inema zayo”."
  26,136,"Abantu ba Huudi bamwamiriye kure bati: “Kuri twebwe rero, ukuduhanura kwawe n’ukutaduhanura, vyose ni co kimwe, ntiturota tukwemera namba!"
  26,137,"Ivyo twemera si ikindi, kiretse ko ari imigenzo y’ab’aho hambere;"
  26,138,"Kandi rero twebwe ntituzohanirwa gukora ivyo utubuza”."
  26,139,"Bararendegeye rero mu guhakana bivuye inyuma, maze Twebwe Allah Duca Tubarungikira igihuhusi c’igikonyozi, Turabahonya. Mu vy’ukuri mw’ihonywa ryabo, ni ukuri harimwo inkebuzo ku bantu. Ntumwa y’Imana! Hamwe n’ivyo rero, abenshi mu bashikiriwe n’iyo nkuru ntibahavuye bakwemera."
  26,140,"Mu vy’ukuri Imana yawe Rurema Allah, ni ukuri ni Yo Nyenintsinzi-Mutaneshwa, Nyenimbabazi ku batoni bayo."
  26,141,"Bene Thamuudi barahakanye bivuye inyuma Intumwa yabo Swalehe, baca bafatwa nk’aho bahakanye Intumwa zose."
  26,142,"Igihe mwenewabo Swalehe yababwira ati: “Ubwo ntimwogamburukira Imana Allah mukubahiriza ibwirizwa ryo kuyisenga ari Imwe Rudende!"
  26,143,"Mu vy’ukuri, jewe kuri mwebwe ndi Intumwa, nkaba n’Umwizigirwa mu vyo ndabashikiriza;"
  26,144,"Enda rero nyabuna nimwikingire ibihano vy’Imana Allah mu kunyemera, muheze munyumvire mu kwubahiriza amabwirizwa yayo;"
  26,145,"Nta n’impembo ndabasavye kw’ishikirizabutumwa ryanje, impembo yanje ndayiziga ku Mana Rurema Allah, Yo Mubungabunzi w’ibiremwa vyose."
  26,146,"Mbega none, Imana yanyu Rurema Allah Ikwiye kubareka mukishira mukizana mu nema Yabahaye kw’isi mutekaniwe!"
  26,147,"Mu mirima itotahaye hamwe n’amazi y’amariba atemba!"
  26,148,"N’ibitara vy’ivyamwa n’ibiterwa hamwe n’itende zoroshe z’akanovera!"
  26,149,"Mukanabaza mu misozi inzu mu buhinga butuma mwiyemera bidasanzwe!"
  26,150,"Kubera ivyo rero, nimwikingire ibihano vy’Imana Allah mu kunyemera, muheze munyumvire mu kwubahiriza amabwirizwa yayo;"
  26,151,"Ntimugakurikire namba ivyo mubwirwa n’abimonogoje mu bugarariji;"
  26,152,"Bagenzwa n’ubwononyi kw’isi, batigera bitwararika gukora ibitunganye”."
  26,153,"Bene Thamuudi barinamuye babwira Swalehe bati: “Ni ukuri wewe, uri mu barozwe koko gushika n’aho utakigira n’ubwo kurahura!"
  26,154,"Wewe nta co uri, kiretse ko uri umuntu nkatwe, udusumbije igiki cotuma uba Intumwa! Enda rero nyabuna zana icemezo cerekana ko uri Intumwa, niwaba koko uri mu mvugakuri ko Imana Allah Yakuturungitseko!”."
  26,155,"Swalehe yababwiye ati: “Ng’iyo ingamiya mwarungikiwe n’Imana Allah, kugira ibabere icemezo cerekana ko ndi mu kuri, yagenewe gushoka ku musi wayo na mwe mukaba murekuriwe kuvoma ku musi uzwi ukurikira;"
  26,156,"Ntimunayikomakome ku nabi ngo muyice imitsi. Nimwahirahira rero mukayikomakoma ku nabi, nta kizobuza ko mushikirwa n’ibihano vy’Imana Allah ku musi uhambaye”."
  26,157,"Ni ho rero bahakana, basimbira kuri nya ngamiya barayica imitsi, barayibaga, maze bazinduka bicuza ku vyo bakoze, bamaze kumenya neza ko bategerezwa guhanwa;"
  26,158,"Baca bashikirwa rero n’ibihano vy’Imana Allah basezeraniwe na Swalehe (nyakugira amahoro y’Imana Allah), birabahonya. Mu vy’ukuri mw’ihonywa rya Bene Thamuudi, ni ukuri harimwo inkebuzo ku wushaka kwikebuka mu bantu. Hamwe n’ivyo rero, abenshi mu bashikiriwe n’iyo nkuru, ntibahavuye bemera Imana Allah."
  26,159,"Mu vy’ukuri Imana yawe Rurema Allah, ni ukuri ni Yo Nyenintsinzi-Mutaneshwa, Nyenimbabazi ku batoni bayo."
  26,160,"Abantu ba Luutwi barahakanye bivuye inyuma Intumwa yabo Luutwi, baca bafatwa nk’aho bahakanye Intumwa zose."
  26,161,"Igihe mwenewabo Luutwi yababwira ati: “Ubwo ntimwogamburukira Imana Allah mukubahiriza amabwirizwa yayo!"
  26,162,"Mu vy’ukuri, jewe kuri mwebwe ndi Intumwa, nkaba n’Umwizigirwa mu vyo ndabashikiriza;"
  26,163,"Enda rero nyabuna nimwikingire ibihano vy’Imana Allah mu kunyemera, muheze munyumvire mu kwubahiriza amabwirizwa yayo;"
  26,164,"Nta n’impembo ndabasavye kw’ishikirizabutumwa ryanje, impembo yanje ndayiziga ku Mana Rurema Allah, Yo Mubungabunzi w’ibiremwa vyose."
  26,165,"Mbega none, karashize ingani mwabirane abagabo ku bagabo muri Bene Adamu!"
  26,166,"Muheze mwirengagize kwabira abo mwaremewe n’Imana yanyu Rurema Allah mu bagore, ari na bo mwagenewe kugira muryoherwe muheze murondoke! Ahubwo rero, mwebwe muri abantu bimonogoje mu kuvogera imbibe z’ibibujijwe n’Imana Allah”."
  26,167,"Abantu Luutwi yarungitsweko bahavuye bamutera ubwoba bati: “Luutwi! Utaretse kutubuza kwabirana abagabo ku bandi, ni ukuri nta kibuza, tuzokwomora utuvire mu gihugu!”."
  26,168,"Luutwi asubizayo ati: “Mu vy’ukuri, jewe ndi mu biyamiriza bivuye inyuma bakanashavuzwa cane n’ivyo mukora”."
  26,169,"Luutwi amaze kwihebura ko batarota bamwumvira, yasavye Imana Allah avuga ati: “Mana yanje Rurema Allah! Nkingira jewe hamwe n’umuryango wanje inkurikizi z’ivyaha vy’agahomerabunwa bakora”."
  26,170,"Ni ho rero Twebwe Allah, Twarokora Luutwi hamwe n’umuryango wiwe n’abitabiriye irarikiramana ryiwe;"
  26,171,"Kiretse umukecuru umwe muri bo atemeye, ari na we yari umugore wiwe, yari mu bategerezwa guhanwa;"
  26,172,"Mu nyuma rero, ni ho Twebwe Allah Twarandurana n’imizi abahakanye bakagarariza;"
  26,173,"Maze Tubakurikiza n’icucagirwa ry’amabuye amanuka avuye mu kirere nk’imvura y’urutavanako; ryari icucagirwa ry’amabuye ribi cane ku bihanijwe n’Intumwa bakanka kuzumvira!"
  26,174,"Mu vy’ukuri mw’ihonywa ry’abantu ba Luutwi, ni ukuri harimwo inkebuzo ku bahakanyi bagarariza amabwirizwa y’Imana Allah. Hamwe n’ivyo rero, abenshi muri bo ntibahavuye bemera."
  26,175,"Mu vy’ukuri Imana yawe Rurema Allah, ni ukuri ni Yo Nyenintsinzi-Mutaneshwa, Nyenimbabazi ku batoni bayo."
  26,176,"Abantu bo mu gisagara c’ibiti bitotahaye barahakanye bivuye inyuma Intumwa yabo Shu’ayibu, baca bafatwa nk’aho bahakanye Intumwa zose."
  26,177,"Igihe Shu’ayibu yababwira ati: “Ubwo ntimwogamburukira Imana Allah mukubahiriza amabwirizwa yayo!"
  26,178,"Mu vy’ukuri, jewe kuri mwebwe ndi Intumwa, nkaba n’Umwizigirwa mu vyo ndabashikiriza;"
  26,179,"Enda rero nyabuna nimwikingire ibihano vy’Imana Allah mu kunyemera, muheze munyumvire mu kwubahiriza amabwirizwa yayo;"
  26,180,"Nta n’impembo ndabasavye kw’ishikirizabutumwa ryanje, impembo yanje ndayiziga ku Mana Rurema Allah, Yo Mubungabunzi w’ibiremwa vyose."
  26,181,"Shu’ayibu yabwiye abo yarungitsweko ati: “Enda nimukwize ingero mu gihe mugereye abandi, kandi ntimukagabanye ku ngero mugeresha;"
  26,182,"Mwongere mupimire abantu ku munzani utunganye, ukwiza ibiro;"
  26,183,"Ntimukambure abantu ivyabo ku ngero, ku munzani, n’ibindi; eka ntimukagenzwe n’ubwononyi ubwo ari bwo bwose kw’isi;"
  26,184,"Muheze kandi mwikingire ko mwoshikirwa n’ibihano vy’Iyabaremye mwebwe hamwe n’abakurambere banyu”."
  26,185,"Abantu ba Shu’ayibu bamwishuye bati: “Ni ukuri wewe, uri mu barozwe koko gushika n’aho utakigira n’ubwo kurahura!"
  26,186,"Wewe nta n’ico uri, kiretse ko uri umuntu nkatwe, udusumbije igiki cotuma uba Intumwa! Mbere twibwira ko wewe ata nkeka uri mu babesha ko warungitswe kuba Intumwa;"
  26,187,"Saba rero Imana yawe Allah Itumanurireko ibihano bivuye mw’ijuru biduhonye, niwaba koko uri mu mvugakuri ko ari Yo Yakuturungitseko!”."
  26,188,"Shu’ayibu araheza abishura avuga ati: “Imana yanje Rurema Allah, ni Yo Izi neza ivyo mukora vyotuma Ibahana”."
  26,189,"Bahavuye rero barendegera mu guhakana bivuye inyuma Shu’ayibu, maze Imana Allah Ibahanisha ubushuhe bumena imbwa agahanga, baraheza bahungira nya bushuhe musi y’igicu kibaha agatutu n’akayaga. Bamaze kwiyegeraniriza hamwe bose musi ya nya gicu, ni ho Imana Allah Yaca Irungika umuriro ubaturira bose, mu vy’ukuri cari igihano c’ihonywa ku musi uhambaye."
  26,190,"Mu vy’ukuri, mw’ihonywa ry’abantu bo mu gisagara c’ibiti bitotahaye, ni ukuri harimwo inkebuzo ku bahakanyi bagarariza amabwirizwa y’Imana Allah. Hamwe n’ivyo rero, abenshi muri bo ntibahavuye bikebuka ngo bemere."
  26,191,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Mu vy’ukuri Imana yawe Rurema Allah, ni ukuri ni Yo Nyenintsinzi-Mutaneshwa, Nyenimbabazi ku batoni bayo."
  26,192,"Mu vy’ukuri, iyi Qor’ani icira abantu ku mayange kahise k’ivyashikiye Intumwa n’abo zarungitsweko, Yamanuwe ivuye ku Mana Rurema Allah, Umubungabunzi w’ibiremwa vyose;"
  26,193,"Ntumwa y'Imana! Iyo Qor’ani yamanukanwe na Mutimamweranda akaba n’umwizigirwa Jibrili;"
  26,194,"Araheza arayigusomera urayizigama mu mutima, uranatahura n’ingingo zirimwo, kugira ube Intumwa mu zindi Ntumwa zigabisha abo zarungitsweko ku bihano vy’Imana Allah, uheze ugabishe rero abantu bose co kimwe n’amajini."
  26,195,"Akaba yayimanukanye iri mu rurimi rw’icarabu rutomoye, harimwo ingingo zose nkenerwa mu gutunganya ivy’ubuzima bwo kw’isi n’ivy’ubw’inyuma yo gupfa."
  26,196,"Mu vy’ukuri ivugwa ry’iyi Qor’ani, ni ukuri riri mu Bitabu vy’Intumwa zo hambere yawe."
  26,197,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Mbega abaguhakana, ntivyari bikwiye kubabera icemezo cotuma bemera ko uri Intumwa, kuba abamenyi muri Bene Israyeli bazi neza na neza ko uri Intumwa vy’ukuri, n’uko Qor’ani ari ukuri kudahinyuzwa!."
  26,198,"N'iyo Twebwe Allah Tumanurira Qor’ani bamwe mu batavuga ururimi rw’icarabu;"
  26,199,"Maze bakayisomera abagarariji mu Bakorayishi mu carabu gitomoye, ntibari kuyemera namba, bari no kurondera icitwazo c’ukwo kutemera."
  26,200,"Ni nk’ukwo nyene rero Twebwe Allah, Twateye amakenga yo kutemera Qor’ani mu mitima y’abanyavyaha barenga ku mabwirizwa yacu;"
  26,201,"Ntibarota bemera rero, gushika biboneyeko ibihano bibabaza basezeraniwe;"
  26,202,"Maze nya bihano bibashikire giturumbuka ata vyo bari biteze;"
  26,203,"Baheze bicuze bavuga bati: “Ubwo ntitworindirizwa na gato kugira twigaye ku Mana Allah, duheze tuyemere!”;"
  26,204,"Bahenzwe n’uko Twebwe Allah Dutenyenya kubahana, baraheza bihutira gusaba ko Twobahana!"
  26,205,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Mbega wari uzi ko n’aho abagarariji Twobaha kuryoherwa mu buzima bwo kw’isi imyaka n’iyindi;"
  26,206,"Hanyuma bagashikirwa n’ibihano basezeraniwe;"
  26,207,"Ukuryoherwa muri nya buzima imyaka n’iyindi, ata co kwobamarira mu gihe batarigaya ku Mana Allah icaha c’ibangikanyamana!"
  26,208,"Nta ho vyakabaye rero ko Twebwe Allah, Duhana Tugahonya agacimbiri na kamwe k’abantu b’aho hambere, kiretse ko Twabanza kukarungikira Intumwa zikagabisha ku bihano vyacu;"
  26,209,"Nya Ntumwa rero zigaheza zikibutsa nya gacimbiri kwubahiriza amabwirizwa yacu. Ntitwari kurenganya rero umugwi uwo ari wo wose w’abantu ngo Tuwuhane imbere yuko Tuwurungikira Intumwa."
  26,210,"Nta mashetani yigeze amanurira Qor’ani Intumwa Muhamadi nk’uko abagarariji bibwira;"
  26,211,"Ico kizire rero ku mashetani, eka nta n’ico yoshobora;"
  26,212,"Mu vy’ukuri, ayo mashetani ntashoboye no gusuma urusaku kw’ihishurirwa rya Qor’ani mu gihe imanuwe."
  26,213,"Ntukabangikanye rero Imana Allah mu kuyisenga hamwe n’iyindi mana, wohava uba mu bahanirwa ibangikanyamana."
  26,214,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Gabisha rero ku bihano vy’Imana Allah abari hafi yawe, na canecane mu muryango wawe;"
  26,215,"Uheze worohere mu mvugo n’ingiro abemeramana bagukurikiye, mu kwicisha bugufi no kubumvira impuhwe."
  26,216,"Nibaca kubiri n’ingingo yawe, uraheza ubabwire uti: “Mu vy’ukuri jewe, nditandukanije n’ivyo mukora mw’ibangikanyamana”."
  26,217,"Maze wishimikize unizere Imana Allah, Nyenintsinzi-Mutaneshwa, Nyenimbabazi ku batoni bayo."
  26,218,"Ni Yo Ikubona mu gihe ugira usenge wenyene mu gicugu;"
  26,219,"Ikabona n’ukungene ugira uri kumwe n’abayubamira mw’isengesho, haba mu gihe uhagaze, wunamye, wubamye canke wicaye;"
  26,220,"Mu vy’ukuri Iyo Mana Allah, ni Yo Nyenukwumva, Irumva igisomwa, ininahaza n’itaziramana vyawe; Nyenubumenyikurivyose, Irazi neza ivyo ukora n’ivyo uzirikana."
  26,221,"Bantu! Mbega ndababwire uwururukirwa na shetani uwo ari we?"
  26,222,"Burya shetani, yururukira uwo wese yimonogoza mu kubesha, yuzuye ivyaha muri ba senyagara n’abapfumu;"
  26,223,"Amashetani araheza agasuma urusaku mu kwumviriza inkuru y’ibivugwa mu biremwa vyo mw'ijuru; maze agahereza nya nkuru ba senyagara n’abapfumu, kandi abenshi muri bo barabesha."
  26,224,"Burya n’abivuzi b’amazina bashingira ku kinyoma n’ububeshi, maze abahuvye inzira na bo bakabakurikira;"
  26,225,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Ntiwabonye ko abivuzi b’amazina, bapfa ivyo bavuze batagira intumbero; nk’intungwa yaciye ikiziriko itagira iyo iva n’iyo ija;"
  26,226,"N’uko bavuga ivyo batigera bakora, bakivuga abanyabinyoma, bagatyoza imvugakuri!"
  26,227,"Havuyemwo gusa abivuzi b’amazina bemeye bakanakora n’ivyiza bitegetswe, bakananinahaza batazira cane Imana Allah, bagaheza rero bakivuga amazina mu guharanira ubwislamu no kurwanira Intumwa y'Imana mu kwishura abivuzi b’amazina b’abagarariji. Abirenganije rero mw’ibangikanyamana, bazoteba bamenye ingaruka mbi cane zibarindiriye."
